      "$id": "dc1a6d39-db84-5fe8-9a5e-68f584980150",
      "code": "self.self = /* ? */;\nif ((parent && SSF2API.isReady()) || self.self) {\n\tself.self.setGlobalVariable(\"canStartRise\", true);\n\tself.self.setGlobalVariable(\"jab\", false);\n\tself.self.setGlobalVariable(\"jab2\", false);\n\tif (self.self.getMetalStatus()) {\n\t} else {\n\t\tself.self.playSound(\"mario_dizzy\", true);\n\t}\n}\nreturn;",
